                            Ce projet d’art, fondé par Sellah Alidor (collectif FROM PARIS) et Thibault Chazal
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-3 col-sm-3 col-md-3 col-lg-3">
                            <p> En savoir plus <br> 
                                Charte <br> FAQ <br></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-3 col-sm-3 col-md-3 col-lg-3">
                            <p> Contact <br>
                                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-phone">07 81 02 72 15</span>
                                <br>
                                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"> contact@karism.fr</span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-xs-3 col-sm-3 col-md-3 col-lg-3">
                            <a href="http://placehold.it"><img src="http://placehold.it/60x35"></a>
                            icone resaux sociaux <br> O <br> O <br>

                        </div>
                    </footer>






                    {% block javascripts %}        
                        <script src="{{ asset('script/jquery/jquery.js') }}"></script>
                        <script src="{{ asset('script/js/bootstrap.js') }}"></script>
                        <script src="{{ asset('script/js/angular.min.js') }}"></script>
                    {% endblock %}
                    {% block footer %}

                    {% endblock %}
                </body>
            </html>
